Putting it all together, the complete function looks like this:

```javascript
function filterAndSortEvens(arr) {
    const evenNumbers = arr.filter(num => num % 2 === 0);
    evenNumbers.sort((a, b) => a - b);
    return evenNumbers;
}
```

